<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>물품 등록 - MyMarket</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="container mt-5">
    <h2>새 물품 등록</h2>
    <form action="/products/write" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">상품명</label>
            <input type="text" name="title" class="form-control" required>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">가격</label>
            <input type="number" name="price" class="form-control" required>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">상세 설명</label>
            <textarea name="content" class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">이미지 또는 문서(.txt) 첨부</label>
            <input type="file" name="document" class="form-control">
            <small class="text-muted">이미지를 올리거나, 텍스트 파일을 올리면 내용이 자동으로 본문에 추가됩니다.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">등록하기</button>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">취소</a>
        </div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>